<p style="text-align: justify;">We performed a literature search, querying PubMed with terms related to a variety of surgical specialties and procedures, LMIC country names, and NGOs. Titles and abstracts were reviewed for relevance, and names of NGOs were extracted from resulting full-text articles. We included organizations extracted from a review of charitable platforms in global surgery, a review of global pediatric surgical volunteerism, and a survey of pediatric cardiovascular care organizations. Twitter was also used to find organizations.</p>
